---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact - BeaconGuard">
  <h1>Contact</h1>

  <section class="stack-section">
    <p class="lead">
      Use this channel to request an enterprise governance review with BeaconGuard.
      We are structured around three conversation paths:
      platform fit, design partner engagement, and deployment/trust architecture.
    </p>

    <div class="page-actions">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="mailto:design@beaconguard.dev?subject=Platform%20Briefing%20Request">Request platform briefing</a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="mailto:design@beaconguard.dev?subject=Design%20Partner%20Discussion">Start design partner discussion</a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="/reviewer-kit">Open the Reviewer Kit</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="stack-section">
    <h2>Common review materials</h2>
    <p>
      These review materials can be used to begin a self-serve evaluation before deeper engagement.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Architecture blueprint</li>
      <li>Reviewer walkthrough</li>
      <li>Deployment boundary review</li>
      <li>Design partner briefing</li>
      <li><a href="/control-responsibility-matrix">Review the control responsibility matrix</a></li>
      <li><a href="/sample-decision-record">Review a sample decision record</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="stack-section">
    <h2>Primary discussions</h2>
    <div class="section-grid section-grid--compact">
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Platform briefing</h3>
        <p><a href="/platform">Review platform scope and fit</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Design partner pathway</h3>
        <p><a href="/design-partner-program">Explore design partner engagement</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Deployment and control boundary</h3>
        <p><a href="/deployment">Discuss deployment and governance control architecture</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="muted-copy">
      Please include your primary AI integration pattern and assurance expectations in the first message.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="stack-section">
    <h2>Direct channel</h2>
    <p><a class="btn-primary" href="mailto:design@beaconguard.dev?subject=BeaconGuard%20Inquiry">design@beaconguard.dev</a></p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>